    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179110/extras/acfaed6c9062a4dae9b77cdd7c65f6ea.avif?t=1746888119\" width=614 height=66 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >试玩版公告</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >免费体验版《冬季女孩》现已推出！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在试玩版中，您可以体验游戏的部分精彩内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请感受游戏的独特魅力，我们期待您的热情反馈。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同时，恳请您在体验后为游戏宣传助力，让更多玩家能够享受完整版的乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >简介/特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《冬季女孩》是一部以邂逅来自宇宙的少女&quot;谢雅&quot;为开端的视觉小说。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与对地球知之甚少的她一同约会，共度相互了解的美好时光。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179110/extras/ec5ec9e64a114d152705bc82f0181802.poster.avif?t=1746888119\" width=614 height=664 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179110/extras/ec5ec9e64a114d152705bc82f0181802.webm?t=1746888119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动画过场</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欣赏《冬季女孩》精美的动画过场和巧妙的镜头演出。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与两位女主角共度的特别时刻将在您心中留下难忘的印记。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179110/extras/cb63f93b4e9ec28696ec8b55d4e18a63.poster.avif?t=1746888119\" width=614 height=752 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179110/extras/cb63f93b4e9ec28696ec8b55d4e18a63.webm?t=1746888119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179110/extras/cb63f93b4e9ec28696ec8b55d4e18a63.mp4?t=1746888119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择与结局分支</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过与两位女主角的对话和互动，您将亲自推动故事的发展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自主选择如何与她们相处，说些什么话。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您的每一个选择都将影响故事的走向，带来不同的结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179110/extras/81a4acc7c0d0b4ed62c2f238aa08b789.poster.avif?t=1746888119\" width=614 height=672 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179110/extras/81a4acc7c0d0b4ed62c2f238aa08b789.webm?t=1746888119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179110/extras/81a4acc7c0d0b4ed62c2f238aa08b789.mp4?t=1746888119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富多彩的游戏内容</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过平板电脑与女主角璐美畅聊，在社交网络世界中搜寻关于谢雅的目击报告。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，我们还为您准备了各种有趣的小游戏，丰富您的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个版本保持了原文的主要内容，同时使用了&quot;冬季女孩&quot;作为游戏标题，并对一些表述进行了细微调整，以确保整体风格的一致性和流畅性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179110/extras/835ac0ea4bbee5bf05a0ef39e14c4256.avif?t=1746888119\" width=614 height=644 /></span></p>",
